        <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700 mb-0">
          While we strive to provide safe and reliable DLL files, downloading and installing any 
          system files carries inherent risks. Always create a system restore point before making 
          changes, and verify file hashes when possible. We are not responsible for any damage 
          that may occur from using files downloaded from this site.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
